<p><a name="Film_location" id="Film_location"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Hex_(TV_series)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Film location">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Film location</span></h2>
<p>Hex was filmed at <a href="/wiki/Englefield_House" title="Englefield House" class="mw-redirect">Englefield House</a>, a <a href="/wiki/Tudor" title="Tudor">Tudor</a> manor modified in the 18th and 19th centuries. Several external scenes in Series 2 were filmed in the city of <a href="/wiki/St_Albans" title="St Albans">St Albans</a> (Hertfordshire), using locations such as the city centre, the Cathedral grounds and a small street adjacent to it.</p>
